mass extinctions

00:01:50.790 --> 00:01:53.360 align:middle line:84%
were due to things like comets
or asteroids hitting the Earth

00:01:53.360 --> 00:01:56.580 align:middle line:84%
and destroying the environment
and just wiping out life,

00:01:56.580 --> 00:01:58.420 align:middle line:84%
and then it started
all over again.

00:01:58.420 --> 00:02:01.120 align:middle line:84%
