rate that is equivalent

00:02:03.700 --> 00:02:06.120 align:middle line:90%
to the mass extinction periods.

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:10.067 align:middle line:84%
And the significance is the
source of this mass extinction,

00:02:10.067 --> 00:02:11.900 align:middle line:84%
according to science,
