out of the ocean.

00:02:30.420 --> 00:02:31.260 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: In 30 years?

00:02:31.260 --> 00:02:32.676 align:middle line:84%
>>LIPTON: In about
30 years, yeah.

00:02:32.676 --> 00:02:36.360 align:middle line:84%
