00:03:29.985 --> 00:03:31.110 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wait a minute, yes.

00:03:31.110 --> 00:03:32.020 align:middle line:90%
>>LIPTON: -it's kind of freaky.

00:03:32.020 --> 00:03:32.950 align:middle line:90%
But the fact is this.

00:03:32.950 --> 00:03:35.840 align:middle line:84%
He's really not including
that human consciousness

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:38.570 align:middle line:84%
is a very important part of
the unfolding of this planet.

00:03:38.570 --> 00:03:40.280 align:middle line:84%
And if we change
human consciousness,

00:03:40.280 --> 00:03:42.520 align:middle line:84%
and we have to do
it relatively soon,

00:03:42.520 --> 00:03:45.880 align:middle line:84%
there's a great opportunity
to save what we have

00:03:45.880 --> 00:03:47.870 align:middle line:90%
and then rebuild the garden.

00:03:47.870 --> 00:03:50.060 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So how do you
connect this very important

00:03:50.060 --> 00:03:53.280 align:middle line:84%
conversation that we're
having about evolution

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:56.730 align:middle line:84%
and about our species on
this Earth to what you speak

00:03:56.730 --> 00:04:01.156 align:middle line:84%
about in terms of biology and
cellular biology and science?

00:04:01.156 --> 00:04:02.530 align:middle line:84%
>>LIPTON: Well,
very interesting.

00:04:02.530 --> 00:04:04.571 align:middle line:84%
What we've been finding
out in the recent science

00:04:04.571 --> 00:04:07.920 align:middle line:84%
is that human consciousness,
the way we think

00:04:07.920 --> 00:04:10.710 align:middle line:84%
and the way we behave,
is fundamentally

00:04:10.710 --> 00:04:13.530 align:middle line:84%
controlling the environment
in which we live.

00:04:13.530 --> 00:04:17.680 align:middle line:84%
And so basically, it says
that our belief systems are

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:20.060 align:middle line:84%
very critical to the way
we live in the world.

00:04:20.060 --> 00:04:23.540 align:middle line:84%
So, for example,
today when we are just

00:04:23.540 --> 00:04:27.680 align:middle line:84%
destroying the environment
and making monocultures out

00:04:27.680 --> 00:04:30.710 align:middle line:84%
of what were just beautiful
gardens that the Earth offered,

00:04:30.710 --> 00:04:33.960 align:middle line:84%
this is totally antagonistic
to life on this planet.

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:36.700 align:middle line:84%
The way that we're
polluting the water,

00:04:36.700 --> 00:04:39.470 align:middle line:84%
polluting the air, the
petrochemicals that

00:04:39.470 --> 00:04:42.950 align:middle line:84%
