>>LISA: Is it that high?

01:17:36.530 --> 01:17:37.770 align:middle line:90%
>>LIPTON: It's that high.

01:17:37.770 --> 01:17:38.490 align:middle line:90%
It's that high.

01:17:38.490 --> 01:17:40.540 align:middle line:84%
And so while we're
doing this, please let's

01:17:40.540 --> 01:17:41.914 align:middle line:84%
add the other side
of the picture

01:17:41.914 --> 01:17:44.910 align:middle line:84%
because people always reference
the placebo effect about how

01:17:44.910 --> 01:17:47.410 align:middle line:84%
this positive thinking
