01:17:52.100 --> 01:17:53.510 align:middle line:90%
for this reason.

01:17:53.510 --> 01:17:55.325 align:middle line:84%
There's a word that
science has given it,

01:17:55.325 --> 01:17:56.700 align:middle line:84%
but the public's
not aware of it.

01:17:56.700 --> 01:17:58.020 align:middle line:90%
It's called the nocebo effect.

01:17:58.020 --> 01:18:00.840 align:middle line:90%
Nocebo is a negative thought.

01:18:00.840 --> 01:18:02.590 align:middle line:84%
What is a negative
thought, the influence?

01:18:02.590 --> 01:18:04.340 align:middle line:84%
We only talked about
the positive thought.

01:18:04.340 --> 01:18:05.130 align:middle line:90%
And I go, no, no.

01:18:05.130 --> 01:18:06.960 align:middle line:84%
Science has revealed
that negative thoughts

01:18:06.960 --> 01:18:08.970 align:middle line:84%
and positive thoughts
are equally powerful,

01:18:08.970 --> 01:18:11.020 align:middle line:84%
but they work in
opposite directions.

01:18:11.020 --> 01:18:15.830 align:middle line:84%
A positive thought can heal
you, but a negative thought

01:18:15.830 --> 01:18:17.400 align:middle line:90%
can actually kill you.

01:18:17.400 --> 01:18:20.350 align:middle line:84%
And it's the same
mechanism, it's

01:18:20.350 --> 01:18:22.737 align:middle line:84%
just that the thought is
translated into chemistry.

01:18:22.737 --> 01:18:24.153 align:middle line:84%
The chemistry
matches the thought.

01:18:24.153 --> 01:18:24.944 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Hallelujah!

01:18:24.944 --> 01:18:27.000 align:middle line:90%
This is exactly, yes.

01:18:27.000 --> 01:18:29.890 align:middle line:84%
>>LIPTON: And we have to own
that because psychologists tell

01:18:29.890 --> 01:18:31.590 align:middle line:84%
us that about 70%
of our thoughts

01:18:31.590 --> 01:18:33.540 align:middle line:90%
are negative and redundant.

01:18:33.540 --> 01:18:34.780 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I believe that, yeah.

01:18:34.780 --> 01:18:36.090 align:middle line:84%
>>LIPTON: So it says, just
in your everyday life,

01:18:36.090 --> 01:18:36.690 align:middle line:90%
