>>LIPTON: -chemistry that is
taking away your vitality.

01:18:40.620 --> 01:18:43.340 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And this has to do with
the subconscious mind, though.

01:18:43.340 --> 01:18:45.430 align:middle line:84%
>>LIPTON: The conscious and the
subconscious mind are the two,

01:18:45.430 --> 01:18:47.346 align:middle line:84%
