01:18:52.040 --> 01:18:52.940 align:middle line:90%
There's two parts--

01:18:52.940 --> 01:18:53.690 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Which one?

01:18:53.690 --> 01:18:55.080 align:middle line:84%
>>LIPTON: -to this
mind and each part

01:18:55.080 --> 01:18:57.200 align:middle line:84%
