called the prefrontal cortex.

01:19:30.640 --> 01:19:33.110 align:middle line:84%
And I say, well, what is the
role of the conscious mind?

01:19:33.110 --> 01:19:35.180 align:middle line:84%
Well, I tell you,
the conscious mind

01:19:35.180 --> 01:19:36.530 align:middle line:90%
