01:19:36.530 --> 01:19:37.560 align:middle line:90%
Your personal identity.

01:19:37.560 --> 01:19:38.500 align:middle line:90%
Your spirit.

01:19:38.500 --> 01:19:39.520 align:middle line:90%
Who you are.

01:19:39.520 --> 01:19:41.920 align:middle line:84%
That's coming in from
the conscious mind, OK?

01:19:41.920 --> 01:19:45.480 align:middle line:84%
And I say, OK, that's our
source of personal identity.

01:19:45.480 --> 01:19:48.630 align:middle line:84%
