expressing creativity.

01:19:58.620 --> 01:19:59.120 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

01:19:59.120 --> 01:20:02.580 align:middle line:84%
>>LIPTON: I go, OK, but here's
where the core thing is.

01:20:02.580 --> 01:20:08.840 align:middle line:84%
The conscious mind is the
source of your personal wishes

01:20:08.840 --> 01:20:12.250 align:middle line:84%
and your personal desires,
and your personal aspirations,

01:20:12.250 --> 01:20:13.460 align:middle line:90%
this creative mind.

