So I say, oh, conscious mind
has what you want out of life.

01:20:16.537 --> 01:20:18.370 align:middle line:84%
It has all your wishes
and all your desires.

01:20:18.370 --> 01:20:20.730 align:middle line:84%
So when you're operating
from the conscious mind,

01:20:20.730 --> 01:20:24.756 align:middle line:84%
it's going to feed the system
the chemistry to support

01:20:24.756 --> 01:20:26.130 align:middle line:84%
what you really
want out of life.

01:20:26.130 --> 01:20:27.930 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's where your
goals are located, and that's--

01:20:27.930 --> 01:20:28.090 align:middle line:90%
>>LIPTON: Yeah.

01:20:28.090 --> 01:20:30.464 align:middle line:84%
That's your creat-- because
you haven't acquired them yet

01:20:30.464 --> 01:20:32.650 align:middle line:84%
by definition,
your conscious mind

01:20:32.650 --> 01:20:34.240 align:middle line:84%
